                     <interp inst="t17981024-41-person342" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , the constable, produced the tea-kettle, which was deposed to by the prosecutor).</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. A man in the tap-room gave me sixpence to carry it.</p>
